host_about:
Attentive and hardworking. I love music, traveling, sunbathing and yoga. I speak Spanish, Catalan, English and a little French.
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Detallista y trabajadora. Me encanta la música, viajar, tomar el sol y el yoga. Hablo castellano, catalán, inglés y un poco de francés.

After 9 years working on the tourism area, I decide to dedicate myself to my Dream: being a mother while working full time on our familiar company! 
My goal is to provide a personalized SERVICE and at the same time make you feel just like one more member of the family!

I offer you the privacy like all the other apartments in Barcelona have; 
the same local feeling like all the other apartments in Barcelona have; 
the central location like all the other apartments in Barcelona have; 
but what I believe makes a difference is offer you all this, together with the feeling of having somebody from the family waiting for you on the other side of the world!

So here I am at your disposal, ready to receive you in your home in Barcelona!

Yours sincerely, 
Daniela Escolà da Silva

